 583:src/main.cpp  **** // Slew rates (per sample at 48 kHz)
 584:src/main.cpp  **** // Lower value = faster response.
 585:src/main.cpp  **** // NOTE: pitch glide and the amp attack/release are now per-voice (see Voice
