1151:src/main.cpp  **** 
1152:src/main.cpp  ****             // ‚îÄ‚îÄ Direct exponential frequency mapping across the voice range ‚îÄ‚îÄ
1153:src/main.cpp  ****             // freq = freq_low * (freq_high/freq_low)^pos01
1154:src/main.cpp  ****             //      = freq_low * e^(pos01 * log_freq_ratio)
